    {
      "scene_index": 6,
      "label": "第六场",
      "characters_present": [
        "四龙套",
        "徐庶",
        "徐母",
        "曹操",
        "程昱"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐母上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "曹贼用计将我禁，倒叫老身不安宁。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（程昱、徐庶同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启伯母：元直兄来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩儿叩见母亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！你为何不在新野，扶助刘使君，到此则甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "因奉母亲书信，故而前来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "书信在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在这里。母亲请看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呸！大胆的奴才！想当年你为人报仇，打伤人命，涂面改装，逃出在外。为娘\n因你是一番义气，并不责备于你。以为儿飘荡江湖，学业定有进益，何以反不\n如初？你既读书，须知忠孝不能两全。岂不知曹操本欺君罔上之贼，刘玄德仁\n义布于四海，况又是汉室之胄。今既事之，得其主矣。怎么，你竟凭这一纸伪\n书，不加详察，遂弃明投暗，自取恶名，辱没祖先。即老身死在九泉，也无面\n目，见徐氏三代宗亲。你真气死为娘也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐母急下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母亲息怒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "元直兄，令堂怒气冲冲，去往后堂去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你我同到后堂观看。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐庶拉程昱同下。徐母上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住。吾儿徐庶，被曹贼用假书，将他诓至许昌。我母子中了奸计，何日才能\n出得曹营。也罢！待我悬梁自尽了罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐母",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "曹贼用计心毒狠，\n害得我母子落恶名。\n倒不如悬梁来自尽……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐母闭门自缢。程昱、徐庶同上，踢门，解救。徐庶哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一见母亲把命丧，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（程昱暗下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐庶",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
